  "Title": "Reverse an Array",
  "Description": "Given an array of integers, return the array in reverse order.\n\nFirst line: N. Second line: N integers.\n\n**Example 1:**\n- Input:\n```\n5\n1 2 3 4 5\n```\n- Output: `5 4 3 2 1`\n\n**Constraints:**\n- 1 <= N <= 1,000,000\n- -10,000 <= element <= 10,000\n- Expected complexity: O(n)",
  "Difficulty": 1,
  "TimeLimitMs": 3000,
  "MemoryLimitKb": 131072,
